These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, old-henry
The people have 2 different jobs:  mechanic, teacher
1. the mechanic is in an even position##4
2. the teacher is the old-henry-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Cigar   | old-henry | blend |
| Job     | teacher    | mechanic   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: amber, blood-red
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is sailing is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person who likes amber##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Color   | blood-red | amber        |
| Sport      | sailing  | weightlifting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, fanta
There are 2 different nationalities: canadian, turkish
1. the canadian is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Beverage   | fanta    | mirinda |
| Nationality   | canadian | turkish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, dannemann
There 2 different types of food: broccoli, mango
1. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
2. the person eating mango is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Cigar   | baccarat      | dannemann |
| Food       | broccoli | mango    |

